ac.post_content: Self-expression lies at the heart of every cyclist. In the way they ride, the way they train, in their aspirations, hopes, and goals. Beyond the rhetorical, though, lies something more bottled-up. It’s the crush, for the racing cyclist, of prostituting your own carcass for it.
